                        <head>283. Summary of Conclusions of a Meeting of the Washington Special
                            Actions Group<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d283fn1">Source: National
                                Archives, <persName corresp="#p_NRM1">Nixon</persName> Presidential
                                Materials, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (H-Files), Box
                                H–115, <gloss target="#t_WSAG1">WSAG</gloss> Meetings Minutes,
                                Originals 1971. Top Secret; Sensitive. The meeting took place in the
                                Stuation Room of the White House.</note>
                        </head>
